(audio/play 'tone 130.81 0.5)  ;; C2 (I)
(audio/play 'tone 174.61 0.5)  ;; F2 (IV)
(audio/play 'tone 196.00 0.5)  ;; G2 (V)
(audio/play 'tone 130.81 0.5)  ;; C2 (I)
```
`<!-- BUILD: runnable standalone; bass-note chord progression -->`

**What you hear:** Even without chords, your ear fills in the harmony. These four bass notes sketch the most common progression in Western music.

