(audio/play 'tone 432 3.0)  ;; A4 at 432 Hz (an alternative tuning), three full seconds
```
`<!-- BUILD: runnable standalone; long sustained tone -->`

**What you hear:** A pure, uninterrupted vibration. Three seconds is a long time for a single sine tone — you start to hear the *quality* of the sound, not just the pitch.

