(audio/play 'tone 261.63 0.2)
(audio/play 'tone 329.63 0.2)
(audio/play 'tone 392.00 0.4)
;; Response: falling
(audio/play 'tone 392.00 0.2)
(audio/play 'tone 329.63 0.2)
(audio/play 'tone 261.63 0.4)
```
`<!-- BUILD: runnable standalone; call-and-response phrase pair -->`

**What you hear:** The first phrase \"asks a question\" (rising contour, ends on G, unstable). The second phrase \"answers\" (falling contour, ends on C, stable).

