### A Minor-Key Gesture

The **natural minor scale** has a different pattern of whole and half steps than the major scale. Here's a fragment.

```scheme
;; A minor: A B C D E
(audio/play 'tone 220.00 0.25)  ;; A3
(audio/play 'tone 246.94 0.25)  ;; B3
(audio/play 'tone 261.63 0.25)  ;; C4
(audio/play 'tone 293.66 0.25)  ;; D4
(audio/play 'tone 329.63 0.25)  ;; E4
```
